155
00:11:25,724 --> 00:11:28,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Since they both have the same body,</b></font>

156
00:11:28,064 --> 00:11:30,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>maybe they have similar maneuverability?</b></font>

157
00:11:30,534 --> 00:11:31,964
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I doubt that.</b></font>

158
00:11:31,964 --> 00:11:33,964
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That Eight-Five is a joke,</b></font>

159
00:11:33,964 --> 00:11:37,604
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>compared to the Eight-Six Bunta has built</b></font>

160
00:11:37,604 --> 00:11:40,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and modified over the years.</b></font>

161
00:11:40,544 --> 00:11:42,444
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>A joke?!</b></font>

162
00:11:42,444 --> 00:11:45,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You mean, Takumi can
drive pretty much any car?</b></font>

163
00:11:45,944 --> 00:11:49,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Just as long as they have the FR layout,</b></font>

164
00:11:49,754 --> 00:11:54,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>he can bring out their full potential.</b></font>

165
00:11:54,924 --> 00:11:58,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Not just anyone can drive an Eight-Six.</b></font>

166
00:11:58,764 --> 00:12:02,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You have to have mastered
the basic skills to drive one.</b></font>

167
00:12:02,894 --> 00:12:06,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Bunta used to say...</b></font>

168
00:12:06,364 --> 00:12:09,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>"An Eight-Six trains the driver."</b></font>

169
00:12:34,864 --> 00:12:39,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That car... had a Night Kids sticker on it.</b></font>

170
00:12:39,704 --> 00:12:42,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It had street racing written all over it.</b></font>

171
00:12:42,104 --> 00:12:45,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You can totally tell modified cars from others</b></font>

172
00:12:45,204 --> 00:12:48,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>by looking at how they run.</b></font>

173
00:12:48,574 --> 00:12:50,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah.</b></font>

174
00:12:50,044 --> 00:12:55,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Lately, those Night Kids come to Akina a lot.</b></font>

175
00:12:55,214 --> 00:12:57,954
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What do they want?</b></font>

176
00:12:57,954 --> 00:13:01,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Well, since their leader Nakazato lost,</b></font>

177
00:13:01,994 --> 00:13:04,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't think anyone from their team</b></font>

178
00:13:04,564 --> 00:13:07,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>will come out for a rematch.</b></font>

179
00:13:20,444 --> 00:13:23,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I almost feel bad for him.</b></font>

180
00:13:23,114 --> 00:13:26,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Now that Takeshi has lost to that Eight-Six,</b></font>

181
00:13:26,284 --> 00:13:29,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>he can't act all invincible anymore.</b></font>

182
00:13:29,284 --> 00:13:31,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>May I help you?</b></font>

183
00:13:32,024 --> 00:13:33,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Two coffees.
--Sure.</b></font>

184
00:13:33,454 --> 00:13:39,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I heard that the Eight-Six driver
in the Speed Stars is just a kid.</b></font>

185
00:13:39,524 --> 00:13:42,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't know how good this kid is...</b></font>

186
00:13:42,264 --> 00:13:44,934
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...but when I beat that Eight-Six,</b></font>

187
00:13:44,934 --> 00:13:47,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll be better than Takeshi.</b></font>

188
00:13:47,634 --> 00:13:50,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll be the fastest one in Night Kids.</b></font>

189
00:13:50,874 --> 00:13:52,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't know, Shingo.</b></font>

190
00:13:52,374 --> 00:13:54,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I know you're fast downhill,</b></font>

191
00:13:54,544 --> 00:13:56,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but I've heard this kid is abnormal.</b></font>

192
00:13:56,574 --> 00:14:00,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I know I can take him fair and square,</b></font>

193
00:14:00,314 --> 00:14:02,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but I have a more interesting idea,</b></font>

194
00:14:02,314 --> 00:14:05,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>which will ensure my victory.</b></font>

195
00:14:05,324 --> 00:14:06,824
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Wha...?!</b></font>

196
00:14:06,824 --> 00:14:12,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You'll see. I'll show him an
impressively dangerous downhill.</b></font>

197
00:14:12,694 --> 00:14:16,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The world only needs one downhill specialist.</b></font>

198
00:14:16,864 --> 00:14:19,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The Eight-Six is outdated.</b></font>

199
00:14:19,704 --> 00:14:24,604
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll make sure to send it to a scrap yard.</b></font>

200
00:14:24,604 --> 00:14:26,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Wha...</b></font>

201
00:14:26,544 --> 00:14:29,774
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Shingo Shoji of Night Kids...</b></font>

202
00:14:29,774 --> 00:14:33,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...is the fastest downhill racer in Gunma.</b></font>

203
00:14:53,764 --> 00:14:55,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Where is Ryosuke?</b></font>

204
00:14:55,374 --> 00:14:59,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>My brother is locked in his room,</b></font>

205
00:14:59,044 --> 00:15:01,644
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>staring at his computer screen.</b></font>

206
00:15:01,644 --> 00:15:03,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He sure likes doing that.</b></font>

207
00:15:03,744 --> 00:15:06,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He's the only street racer in Gunma</b></font>

208
00:15:06,914 --> 00:15:10,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>who trains by staring at a computer screen.</b></font>

209
00:15:14,654 --> 00:15:17,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I wonder what would happen if my brother</b></font>

210
00:15:17,394 --> 00:15:20,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and the Eight-Six of Mount Akina raced?</b></font>

211
00:15:20,394 --> 00:15:24,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There is no way Ryosuke would lose to him.</b></font>

212
00:15:26,604 --> 00:15:30,774
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Ryosuke knows all about that Eight-Six now.</b></font>

213
00:15:30,774 --> 00:15:34,444
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm sure he has all the data he needs</b></font>

214
00:15:34,444 --> 00:15:37,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>to create a simulation of
a winning race in his head.</b></font>

215
00:15:41,914 --> 00:15:45,784
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No street racer knows more
about cars than my brother.</b></font>

216
00:15:45,784 --> 00:15:47,954
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I can't imagine him losing,</b></font>

217
00:15:47,954 --> 00:15:51,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>considering his exceptional skills.</b></font>

218
00:15:51,194 --> 00:15:53,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Well, then...</b></font>

219
00:15:53,194 --> 00:15:57,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But that Eight-Six won't lose, either.</b></font>

220
00:15:59,104 --> 00:16:02,304
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That high-speed drifting...</b></font>

221
00:16:02,304 --> 00:16:05,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...and his delicate brake control.</b></font>

222
00:16:05,004 --> 00:16:07,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He's exceptional, too.</b></font>

223
00:16:07,974 --> 00:16:10,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>As a fellow FR driver,</b></font>

224
00:16:10,574 --> 00:16:14,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I may have fallen for the
way that Eight-Six runs.</b></font>

225
00:16:14,554 --> 00:16:16,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Keisuke...</b></font>

226
00:16:16,054 --> 00:16:18,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If they race, one will lose.</b></font>

227
00:16:18,654 --> 00:16:21,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't want my brother to lose,</b></font>

228
00:16:21,194 --> 00:16:26,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but I don't want to see
that Eight-Six lose, either.</b></font>

229
00:16:26,224 --> 00:16:28,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Strange, isn't it?</b></font>

230
00:16:30,264 --> 00:16:32,604
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Oh, sorry!</b></font>

231
00:16:32,604 --> 00:16:34,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Did you get wet?
--No.</b></font>

232
00:16:34,674 --> 00:16:37,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Hold on...
--Sure.</b></font>

233
00:16:37,174 --> 00:16:42,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Why don't we go somewhere together again?</b></font>

234
00:16:43,544 --> 00:16:45,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We can go to the mountains,</b></font>

235
00:16:45,944 --> 00:16:48,954
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>or the highlands, or the ocean.</b></font>

236
00:16:48,954 --> 00:16:52,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--We're on summer vacation!
--Yeah...</b></font>

237
00:16:53,684 --> 00:16:56,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Let's make a lot of memories!</b></font>

238
00:16:56,094 --> 00:16:58,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We should.</b></font>

239
00:16:58,364 --> 00:17:02,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi, I wouldn't mind going with you...</b></font>

240
00:17:02,894 --> 00:17:05,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...on an overnight trip.</b></font>

241
00:17:13,474 --> 00:17:17,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>When is your next day off? This Sunday?</b></font>

242
00:17:17,044 --> 00:17:20,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It depends, really...</b></font>

243
00:17:20,714 --> 00:17:24,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Do you want to take me for a drive again then?</b></font>

244
00:17:25,384 --> 00:17:29,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--With that car?
--Yeah.</b></font>

245
00:17:31,924 --> 00:17:36,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No blowing me off this time, Takumi!</b></font>

246
00:17:36,164 --> 00:17:40,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Do you mind if Itsuki joins us?</b></font>

247
00:17:40,104 --> 00:17:42,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The three of us?</b></font>

248
00:17:42,434 --> 00:17:44,444
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I was hoping...</b></font>

249
00:17:44,444 --> 00:17:47,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...you could find someone for him.</b></font>

250
00:17:47,844 --> 00:17:49,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah...</b></font>

251
00:17:49,414 --> 00:17:54,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He's a good guy, but he's shy.</b></font>

252
00:17:54,014 --> 00:17:58,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I didn't know you were so thoughtful.</b></font>

253
00:17:58,384 --> 00:18:02,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I just thought it would be good for him...</b></font>

254
00:18:03,324 --> 00:18:06,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Thank you very much!</b></font>

255
00:18:06,164 --> 00:18:09,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Sure, I'll ask around.</b></font>

256
00:18:09,564 --> 00:18:11,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Thanks.</b></font>

257
00:18:11,804 --> 00:18:16,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm sure I'll find someone perfect for Itsuki.</b></font>

258
00:18:46,364 --> 00:18:48,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That was awesome!</b></font>

259
00:18:48,104 --> 00:18:50,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Maybe I should try it, too.</b></font>

260
00:18:50,334 --> 00:18:54,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm getting the hang of
moving the rear sideways.</b></font>

261
00:18:54,074 --> 00:18:57,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's all about the timing.</b></font>

262
00:18:57,274 --> 00:19:02,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You pull the emergency brake to start the drift.</b></font>

263
00:19:02,484 --> 00:19:04,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But, Iketani...</b></font>

264
00:19:04,214 --> 00:19:08,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I didn't see Takumi pull the emergency brake</b></font>

265
00:19:08,054 --> 00:19:10,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>even once the other night.</b></font>

266
00:19:10,154 --> 00:19:13,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi uses the foot pedal brake</b></font>

267
00:19:13,394 --> 00:19:15,134
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>to shift the weight.</b></font>

268
00:19:15,134 --> 00:19:18,964
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Don't worry, you're a long way from that!</b></font>

269
00:19:18,964 --> 00:19:20,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah...</b></font>

270
00:19:20,064 --> 00:19:23,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We usually go into a
corner and then accelerate</b></font>

271
00:19:23,174 --> 00:19:26,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>to skid the rear tires right before coming out,</b></font>

272
00:19:26,004 --> 00:19:29,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but that's an elementary
technique called Power Slide</b></font>

273
00:19:29,544 --> 00:19:32,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and is not a true drift.</b></font>

274
00:19:32,384 --> 00:19:38,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"Keiichi Tsuchiya's Drift Lesson"</b></font>

275
00:19:32,414 --> 00:19:36,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi drifts into a corner
and controls the skid at the end</b></font>

276
00:19:36,884 --> 00:19:39,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>to stabilize the car--a true drift.</b></font>

277
00:19:39,754 --> 00:19:44,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's the fastest way to turn,
and it looks good, too.</b></font>

278
00:19:44,494 --> 00:19:48,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I see. You've done some research.</b></font>

279
00:19:48,494 --> 00:19:53,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I was bored while my S13 was in the shop,</b></font>

280
00:19:53,034 --> 00:19:55,604
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>so I read some books.</b></font>

281
00:19:55,604 --> 00:19:58,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I wanna try the sidespin, too.</b></font>

282
00:19:58,344 --> 00:20:00,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm so excited!</b></font>

283
00:20:00,344 --> 00:20:04,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I think I'm ready for the next step.</b></font>

284
00:20:04,244 --> 00:20:06,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Instead of a straight line,</b></font>

285
00:20:06,084 --> 00:20:08,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll try it in a low-speed turn.</b></font>

286
00:20:08,284 --> 00:20:11,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Good luck, Iketani!</b></font>

287
00:20:12,224 --> 00:20:14,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Watch out for other cars!</b></font>

288
00:20:14,424 --> 00:20:17,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We'll be there later!</b></font>

289
00:20:30,074 --> 00:20:34,774
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>It's really hard to be in</i>
<i>total control of your car.</i></b></font>

290
00:20:34,774 --> 00:20:37,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I wish I could be like Takumi.</i></b></font>

291
00:20:38,614 --> 00:20:42,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I wanna ride with him one more time.</i></b></font>

292
00:20:42,254 --> 00:20:45,784
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Watching him drive my car</i></b></font>

293
00:20:45,784 --> 00:20:49,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>is the best way to learn.</i></b></font>

294
00:20:49,454 --> 00:20:51,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What?</b></font>

295
00:20:53,064 --> 00:20:55,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I wasn't paying attention...</i></b></font>

296
00:20:55,664 --> 00:20:57,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Darn!</i></b></font>

297
00:21:04,704 --> 00:21:06,774
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You hit my bumper!</b></font>

298
00:21:06,774 --> 00:21:11,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Now I really can't let you go!</b></font>

299
00:21:11,014 --> 00:21:13,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Pass me if you can!</b></font>

300
00:21:23,694 --> 00:21:25,784
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"Mt. Akina Skate Center"</b></font>

301
00:21:51,484 --> 00:21:53,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Speed Stars?!</b></font>

302
00:22:05,864 --> 00:22:07,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>That was close...</i></b></font>

303
00:22:11,344 --> 00:22:17,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>A little tap on the bumper right before a turn...</b></font>

304
00:22:17,344 --> 00:22:21,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's all you need to destabilize a pathetic FR.</b></font>

305
00:22:43,774 --> 00:22:46,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>My pride says you gotta be wild and tough</i></b></font>

306
00:22:46,474 --> 00:22:48,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>So no one intervenes</i></b></font>

307
00:22:48,544 --> 00:22:50,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Never stop, I don't want to stop</i></b></font>

308
00:22:50,074 --> 00:22:52,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Even if you cry because of a sacrificed love</i></b></font>

309
00:22:52,144 --> 00:22:53,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Aim for the peak, sweep the winding street</i></b></font>

310
00:22:53,944 --> 00:22:56,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Beep beep! The warning chime is so cheap!</i></b></font>

311
00:22:56,154 --> 00:22:57,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>The sheep should clear the road</i></b></font>

312
00:22:57,614 --> 00:23:00,054
